text: Joseph Castiglioni (27 September 1877 - 7 June 1959) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:1959 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Oran
